name: Copy data from Azure FHIR service to Azure FHIR service
description:
Copies FHIR resources of specified resource type, from source Azure FHIR service to destination Azure FHIR service.
This supports data copy from:
* Azure API for FHIR (Gen1) to Azure API for FHIR (Gen1)
* Azure API for FHIR (Gen1) to Azure FHIR Service (Gen2)
* Azure FHIR Service (Gen2) to Azure FHIR Service (Gen2)
author: Microsoft
